Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.63,0:00:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.53,0:00:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的一集马上要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.90,0:00:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.07,0:00:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家乡与家人全被歼灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.77,0:00:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟琥珀又落在奈落的手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.41,0:00:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不管珊瑚多么灰心失意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.28,0:00:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最贴心的小猫  云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.08,0:00:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始终陪在她的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师加上珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.65,0:00:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.95,0:00:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.15,0:00:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.03,0:00:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.13,0:00:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.94,0:00:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.04,0:00:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.94,0:00:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.32,0:01:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.82,0:01:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.13,0:01:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.97,0:01:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.20,0:01:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.71,0:01:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.98,0:01:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.98,0:01:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.99,0:01:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.96,0:01:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.08,0:02:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟随我们同行的云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.08,0:02:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一只有两条尾巴的叉尾猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.59,0:02:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要战斗的时候\N它会变得非常大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.39,0:02:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以在空中\N自由飞来飞去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.76,0:02:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时它却是一只\N非常可爱的小猫咪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.33,0:02:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母的脾气非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.96,0:02:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算大家对它不好\N它也是逆来顺受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过必要时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好也让大家知道一下\N你也是有脾气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.54,0:02:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.04,0:02:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第97话 云母为什么没回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.07,0:02:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母  云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.13,0:02:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有没有人看见云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.17,0:02:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看见耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.47,0:02:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.47,0:02:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.21,0:03:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一早起来\N就没有看到它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.68,0:03:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会出去散步了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.95,0:03:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是云母从来不会不说一声\N就自己跑出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是离家出走了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.39,0:03:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会正在发情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.46,0:03:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看恐怕是叛逆期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.76,0:03:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在胡说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.13,0:03:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意让珊瑚担心\N对你们有什么好处嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.23,0:03:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过昨天云母\N看起来真的没有什么异常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.63,0:03:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过溜出去逛逛\N不需要大惊小怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.24,0:03:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果连这种事也要瞎操心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.27,0:03:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们岂不是\N要忙得不可开交了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.48,0:03:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就别管它了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.11,0:03:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等它玩够了自然会回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.28,0:03:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别太担心了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母又不是小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.68,0:03:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.39,0:03:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换了是别的小孩子\N就又另当别论了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.62,0:03:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说也是有道理啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.26,0:03:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这什么意思  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.59,0:03:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就只有\N你一个小孩子而已嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇姑娘  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.70,0:04:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤鱼已经可以吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁说云母马上就会回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.09,0:04:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在连个影子都没看到嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少罗唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.46,0:04:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道它什么时候回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这什么话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己说过的话\N这么快就忘光啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.97,0:04:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么  臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.54,0:04:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.11,0:04:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到外面去找云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.35,0:04:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样漫无目的到处找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.55,0:04:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕也毫无头绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是由犬夜叉上场吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  是要干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是云母吃饭的盘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开猫罐头喂它的时候用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿这个给我要干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.43,0:05:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为\N你最好闻清楚盘子里的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.37,0:05:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母身上的味道\N我会不知道吗 哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好加油  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?闻出来了没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  味道在途中消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.15,0:05:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只爬了三步就不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.89,0:05:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.59,0:05:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是大家分头找好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.09,0:05:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过没用啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.96,0:05:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母的味道突然消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.03,0:05:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就表示它飞上空中了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.23,0:05:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.03,0:05:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这附近\N根本就没有它的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.53,0:05:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不能够\N什么事都不做对吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点我当然懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.47,0:05:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.54,0:05:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有什么线索可以参考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.55,0:05:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比方说你跟云母吵过架啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.98,0:05:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是云母\N是不是附近有认识的朋友啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.78,0:05:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想想总会有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.49,0:05:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样问我我也不知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么细节都可以哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.56,0:06:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比方说吃东西没有胃口啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.19,0:06:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近脾气特别古怪啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.93,0:06:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是附近出现了一些野猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.63,0:06:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…或许是因为我害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.00,0:06:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没有理会云母的感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.44,0:06:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都让云母\N卷入我跟妖怪的决斗之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.37,0:06:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到远方去\N我就理所当然的骑着它上路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.38,0:06:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有奖励赞美过它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.71,0:06:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连它最喜欢吃的鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有常常给它吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.82,0:06:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  别太责怪自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母不会为了这些事离家出走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.89,0:06:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.73,0:06:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到云母\N为什么离家出走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.16,0:06:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.03,0:06:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为刚刚犬夜叉欺负我\N才让我想起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.03,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要随便想想\N就可以知道原因何在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.24,0:06:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底为什么?你快说  七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.41,0:06:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母它…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母是因为犬夜叉还有你们害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.61,0:07:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会离家出走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.42,0:07:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再废话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.68,0:07:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么话快说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.25,0:07:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.92,0:07:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是这个样子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.62,0:07:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.56,0:07:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们大家手捂着胸口\N好好反省一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.56,0:07:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是真的从来没有做过\N对不起云母的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们当中\N有谁谁敢这样断言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以发誓我没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想不起来\N曾经做过什么事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.28,0:07:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们对云母做过哪些过分的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.52,0:07:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就让我一件件\N说给你们听吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.45,0:07:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.65,0:07:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.22,0:07:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一次犬夜叉\N为了学会爆破流技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.39,0:07:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让云母陪他一起练风之伤对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.03,0:07:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练风之伤那一次啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.69,0:08:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.63,0:08:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.20,0:08:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母  要不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.51,0:08:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.38,0:08:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秃掉了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.92,0:08:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…这个自然自己就会好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧不要紧啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.49,0:08:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来  吃饭吃饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.79,0:08:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.00,0:08:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有这回事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.30,0:09:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了\N那阵子的确有这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你以为\N可以这样神不知鬼不觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.67,0:09:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母离家出走一定是因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.28,0:09:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉!都是你害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.68,0:09:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来云母的秃头\N是你造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来  云母…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.42,0:09:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.16,0:09:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能这样就断定\N云母离家出走跟我有关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况\N这件事情已经发生那么久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.03,0:09:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母一定早就忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.83,0:09:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道还会有其他原因吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.33,0:09:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样  说不定真的有喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.20,0:09:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师\N你可别说你也忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.71,0:09:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.34,0:09:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.08,0:09:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  村子里有好多年轻小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.72,0:09:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子云母可以派上用场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.23,0:09:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母  去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪来的小猫  好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.47,0:10:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只猫叫作云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.20,0:10:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我养的宠物猫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.61,0:10:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.84,0:10:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几位姑娘也是\N一样可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  法师你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.88,0:10:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不只这样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.75,0:10:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你就是上次那位法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.12,0:10:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上\N你一定要留在村子里过夜哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.12,0:10:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边请吧  法师\N到我家怎样啊  法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.26,0:10:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  又该云母上场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.50,0:10:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.87,0:10:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶灵  退散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.64,0:10:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了  弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.28,0:10:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒  你这家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.15,0:10:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是啦  这是因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  真是伤脑筋耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母它是我们的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.39,0:11:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们居然\N当它是道具一样使用方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后不可以再有这样的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.30,0:11:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你就从没\N当云母是道具一样使用方便吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.93,0:11:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?咦咦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.65,0:11:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.82,0:11:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  到底什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.69,0:11:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.95,0:11:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道又要什么“考试”啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.55,0:11:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.19,0:11:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.29,0:11:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.33,0:11:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好舒服啊\N拜托你了 云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.57,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你肯帮我完成心愿的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就请你吃比目鱼\N跟鲔鱼口味的猫罐头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.44,0:11:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.68,0:11:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.85,0:12:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.08,0:12:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底回家干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.12,0:12:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.36,0:12:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.99,0:12:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你在这边等我一下下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.73,0:12:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就会回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母  你一定要等我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.24,0:12:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看这样\N大家先来切蛋糕好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.34,0:12:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那就先来切蛋糕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.38,0:12:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.51,0:12:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷  祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.98,0:12:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.25,0:12:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然赶回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.62,0:12:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么犬夜叉哥哥\N没跟你一起回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.39,0:12:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  爷爷\N这是送给你的生日礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.23,0:12:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜喔  这个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是很清楚它的来源啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.03,0:12:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这个跟河童的手不一样\N如假包换的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.27,0:12:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能不能多留一下下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.67,0:12:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为难得爷爷过生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.04,0:12:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少大家一起吃个饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.04,0:13:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为难得爷爷过生日嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为难得嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.91,0:13:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为难得嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.65,0:13:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为难得嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且\N答应云母带罐头回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也忘得一干二净了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.76,0:13:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连戈薇也这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.53,0:13:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.07,0:13:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这几个坏蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.30,0:13:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后不准你们\N再虐待可爱的小妖怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.54,0:13:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.04,0:13:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.21,0:13:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后如果你再敢用拳头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打我任何一拳的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.81,0:13:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就罚你整整一个礼拜\N都不准吃忍者餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.41,0:13:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去  别自己订罚则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.18,0:13:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.32,0:13:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  你千万不要误会\N我们只不过是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.42,0:13:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起  我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.33,0:13:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我并没有恶意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.10,0:13:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.46,0:13:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实\N我又有什么立场指责你们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.33,0:13:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别这么说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你们没什么不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.47,0:14:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上睡不着的时候\N心烦意乱的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.34,0:14:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会叫云母\N带我飞过午夜的山岭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些真的没什么大不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.58,0:14:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才过分呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.75,0:14:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炉火升不起来的时候\N我就叫云母变身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.98,0:14:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的时候\N一天里面好几次让它去冒险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.09,0:14:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它明明睡着了\N我却捏它的鼻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.35,0:14:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了好玩\N还要它陪我玩变装游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.82,0:14:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们几个几乎一点都不疼它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.73,0:14:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们简直坏透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是个愚蠢的人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.90,0:15:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的以为能够\N平安穿过我的势力范围吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.54,0:15:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.04,0:15:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这座森林实在太缺食物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.28,0:15:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是云母呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.15,0:15:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是一只狒狒妖怪\N再加上个大叔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大叔  快点走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.40,0:15:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…又是个妖怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.57,0:15:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.44,0:15:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.94,0:15:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好大的胆子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.94,0:15:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢放走我的猎物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.94,0:15:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.94,0:15:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.18,0:15:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.21,0:15:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.41,0:15:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过\N我确实闻到了云母的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.58,0:15:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一个一个来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.95,0:15:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.09,0:16:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我送给云母的丝巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.60,0:16:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不只是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.73,0:16:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.93,0:16:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林里到处都是动物的骸骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.24,0:16:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.94,0:16:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死妖怪!你把云母给吃了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.98,0:16:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笨蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.11,0:16:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃的动物这么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.98,0:16:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪还记得吃过谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说真的是你吃的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.99,0:16:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用太难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们很快就可以见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.59,0:16:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上进我的肚子来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.96,0:16:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.64,0:16:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整座森林都是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.27,0:16:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林里的一切全都归我管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.78,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.01,0:16:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.38,0:17:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用树枝的反作用力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后灵活进行快速移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.28,0:17:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.02,0:17:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从绝对有利的制高点进行攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.42,0:17:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚妖怪说的话\N也不全是吓唬我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.12,0:17:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候要是云母在就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.94,0:17:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它叫云母?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.94,0:17:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.10,0:17:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后要靠你照顾它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.71,0:18:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.12,0:18:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是只慌张得\N到处乱窜的杂碎妖怪嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种家伙我一下就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不放过你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.49,0:18:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要替云母报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.74,0:18:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭这种打断树枝的本事\N也想要跟我斗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.94,0:19:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.78,0:19:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我觉得以前\N我们真的该对云母好一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.35,0:19:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母已经…呜呜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.82,0:19:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃啊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.45,0:19:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.69,0:19:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.86,0:19:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.69,0:19:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你平安无事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.20,0:19:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.97,0:19:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.32,0:19:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  害我们担心死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.09,0:19:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.03,0:20:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好久不见了\N犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.84,0:20:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥加爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.34,0:20:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.34,0:20:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刀刀斋吩咐我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.01,0:20:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带一块磨刀石\N来给犬夜叉少爷磨铁碎牙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.28,0:20:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨刀石?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么\N把这么重的东西搬来的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.62,0:20:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  不是很简单吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜托云母帮我搬来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.29,0:20:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是专程到这来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.89,0:20:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑在云母身上回到刀刀斋那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.93,0:20:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着马上再赶回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.59,0:20:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一把老骨头差点没散掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.03,0:20:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母  好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.13,0:20:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然来找你\N想请你帮个忙行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.64,0:20:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么  半夜三更叫什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.14,0:20:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝\N我要云母帮我点忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得帮我\N跟犬夜叉他们说一声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.38,0:20:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看  只要一天的功夫\N就能赶回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.38,0:20:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.62,0:21:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.65,0:21:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条丝巾是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.06,0:21:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条丝巾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么  云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.10,0:21:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间\N在这儿逗留玩耍哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.41,0:21:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整件事就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.65,0:21:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.85,0:21:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.82,0:21:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…也许…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.93,0:21:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我睡得太熟所以忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.20,0:21:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么你睡得太熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.20,0:21:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好给我觉悟了  七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.43,0:21:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我啊  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.20,0:21:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.17,0:21:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见好就收吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.61,0:21:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.71,0:21:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.94,0:21:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.61,0:22:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑  七宝\N不要嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.49,0:22:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.70,0:22:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.97,0:22:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.48,0:22:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.72,0:22:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.26,0:22:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.00,0:23:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.24,0:23:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默默承受伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.95,0:23:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会失去一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.52,0:23:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.93,0:23:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的歌才是我的路标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.62,0:23:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.99,0:23:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪里不舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.33,0:23:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一起离开这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.03,0:23:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.06,0:23:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经失去了死魂\N你别理我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.80,0:23:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只有你一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.07,0:23:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定还有机会活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.80,0:23:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么容易放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.34,0:23:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要离开这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.57,0:23:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定要同心协力才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.57,0:23:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.01,0:24:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山洞里只有桔梗跟戈薇两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.31,0:24:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一股充满血气的温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.75,0:24:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这就是戈薇的威力吗


